      <title>市场综述：亚洲股市在财报公布前追随美国股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者的目光不再局限于乔·拜登结束连任竞选，而是关注科技股财报季的开始，亚洲股市跟随华尔街股市反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 22:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司增持比亚迪股份，持股比例降至 5% 以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/berkshire-hathaway-sells-more-of-byd-bringing-stake-below-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司又一次抛售了比亚迪股份，持股比例从两年前的20%以上降至5%以下，此后，比亚迪股价出现三周多来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/berkshire-hathaway-sells-more-of-byd-bringing-stake-below-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
